  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of BKM120 in Relapsed and Refractory NHL</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-label Phase II Study of BKM120 in Patients With Relapsed and Refractory Diffuse Large B-cell Lymphoma, Mantle Cell Lymphoma and Follicular Lymphoma</official_title>
