  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a phase II study evaluating the safety, tolerability and efficacy of BKM120 in
      patients with relapsed or refractory diffuse large B-cell lymphoma (DLBCL), mantle cell
      lymphoma (MCL) or follicular lymphoma (FL).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
